01:43:13.000 --> 01:43:19.000
One either Mitchell or Catherine Adams.

01:43:19.000 --> 01:43:20.000
And...

01:43:20.000 --> 01:43:26.000
These were all the kind of adult advisors.

01:43:26.000 --> 01:43:34.000
And when any and everything would go down in any major kind of way,

01:43:34.000 --> 01:43:37.000
they would have something to say or some advice to give,

01:43:37.000 --> 01:43:40.000
it wasn't always taken.

01:43:40.000 --> 01:43:45.000
Like we would use Bascomb's church a lot.

01:43:45.000 --> 01:43:49.000
I had to report to Miss Adams as a secretary,

01:43:49.000 --> 01:43:53.000
which used a secretary to the advisory group.

01:43:53.000 --> 01:44:01.000
