I didn't have to do none.

01:44:30.000 --> 01:44:34.000
Just find my group and just be with them.

01:44:34.000 --> 01:44:38.000
And would you remember them that day?

01:44:38.000 --> 01:44:45.000
Singing and eating good food.

01:44:45.000 --> 01:44:50.000
And just having a good time that day.

01:44:50.000 --> 01:44:53.000
I paid too much to the speaking.

