Nag was a lot of people.

01:47:52.000 --> 01:47:58.000
Well, that point in time was Nag and then it was Nashville.

01:47:59.000 --> 01:48:07.000
Several hubs, there was Atlanta and there was a lot of competition between these folks too.

01:48:07.000 --> 01:48:09.000
Who else?

01:48:09.000 --> 01:48:12.000
Well, I mean.

01:48:12.000 --> 01:48:16.000
